 \int_1^a \ln (x) dx = \lim_{n \to +\infty} S_n = \ln (a)^2 \lim_{n \to + \infty} \left[ \frac{1}{n} \sum_{k=1}^n \frac{k}{n} a^{\frac{k}{n}} \right].
